* Heeren, Arnold Hermann Ludwig. &quot;Historical researches into the politics, intercourse, and trade of the principal nations of antiquity&quot; (HG Bohn, 1847). online
* Heeren, Arnold Hermann Ludwig. &quot;Historical Researches into the Politics, intercourse, and Trade of the Carthaginians, Ethiopians and Egyptians&quot; (HG Bohn, 1857). online

