<doc id="204123" wikidata="Q5110281" url="?curid=204123" title="Christian Wolf">
<text>Christian Wolf is a German designer of board games. He has won the As d&#x27;Or for &quot;Tutankhamen&quot; and the Kinderspiel des Jahres for &quot;Klondike&quot; in 2001; both were collaborations with Stefanie Rohner. Wolf is an entrepreneur and shareholder &amp; CEO of Anduud City FC in Mongolia.

